{"tid":1369484,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[傳真社] 重組612。警方開槍報細數","createTime":"2019-07-26T17:00:52.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-27T04:35:09.000Z","uid":392,"like":58,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":17,"replies":[{"pid":"ca68099ce6ed80af5d26985529ac71ea200b9432","tid":1369484,"uid":392,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-26T17:00:52.000Z","msg":"612警方暴力驅散示威者，政府堅拒成立獨立調查委員會。但至今44日，警方只公布曾使用「數發」橡膠子彈，未有準確數字。傳真社翻查近200段影片，發現警方最少發射10槍橡膠子彈，而且全部沒有先舉橙旗警示。傳真社就此向警方查詢，截稿前未有回覆。<br />\n足本報道：<a href=\"https://bit.ly/2Y7N4PE\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fbit.ly%2F2Y7N4PE&d=vhywW4AIbf33TEOu71%2FwU9HbQOt8JOG57pMmRaSdLYE%3D&h=8402aa1d\" target=\"_blank\">https://bit.ly/2Y7N4PE</a><br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/factwire/videos/2438662169712563/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Ffactwire%2Fvideos%2F2438662169712563%2F&d=vhywW4AIbf33TEOu71%2FwU9HbQOt8JOG57pMmRaSdLYE%3D&h=912e7de9\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/factwire/videos/2438662169712563/</a>"},{"pid":"36f10d0e86e24d079ee32b0770938343b4c4f593","tid":1369484,"uid":269711,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-26T17:03:37.000Z","msg":"推。<br />\n傳真社有料到！"},{"pid":"2cf642a3a370ffd2d11b049738900879b1ace3ce","tid":1369484,"uid":279650,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-26T17:05:49.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"e5690424743a11299b4ecc643c7168a47b683878","tid":1369484,"uid":105511,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-26T17:15:32.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6baf10c9078414268608d8eb918a626e55e661ba","tid":1369484,"uid":30647,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-26T17:16:58.000Z","msg":"傳真社 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /